      • save

        public void save()
        Method which saves visitor. There are listed 4 cases: 1. Visitor's cookiesId & cookiesData are equal to visitor's MD5_ID & MD5_DATA into HBase. 2. Visitor's cookiesId are equal to MD5_ID from HBase, but DATA is not equal. The we update visitor. 3. Visitor's cookies does not have cookiesId or cookiesData. If visitor's md5Data is found into HBase, then we assign visitor to existing one. 4. Visitor's cookies does not have cookiesId or cookiesData. Create new visitor if nothing similar found into Hbase.
        Specified by:
        save in class com.edgars.table.Table
